# module lib

Renders a library scope declaration as an XML context wrapper. Identical structure to app and module — the type attribute distinguishes them for the model.

# entity Output

```markdown
<system_context type="LIB"{{#name}} name="{{name}}"{{/name}}>

{{body}}

</system_context>
```

# rule

- name is optional. When present it renders as the `name` attribute; when absent the attribute is omitted.
- The closing `</system_context>` tag must always be present on its own line with a blank line before it.
